</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 2</b></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Jul 09, 13:00 to Jul 10, 13:00 &amp; Jul 16, 13:00 to Jul 17, 13:00</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><b>Day 3</b></td>
